comments.comment: Delicious food recipe that will make us soo hungry!!
This is a delicious twist ,and is VERY easy to make.

I used garlic naan bread, mild Italian sausage, and my homemade marinara sauce.  I must say that the ricotta in the cheese base really does make this taste a bit like lasagna. The mozzarella on top did take a while to brown up, so I'll bump up the temperature to 400° next time.   Quick and easy lunch today....and tasty, too!",
